age</code></strong> プロパティは、サーバーからメッセージが届いたときに呼び出されるイベントハンドラー (<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code>) です。これは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> で呼び出されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>aWebSocket</em>.onmessage = function(event) {\n  console.debug(\"WebSocket message received:\", event);\n};</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98\"><code>EventListener</code></a> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#handler-websocket-onmessage\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">WebSocket: onmessage の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.WebSocket.onmessage","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"値","id":"value"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"WebSocket.onmessage プロパティは、サーバーからメッセージが届いたときに呼び出されるイベントハンドラー (event handler) です。これは MessageEvent で呼び出されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSo